(40, 21, 20, 41, 11, 20, 21, 'fig tree withered away', 'Fig Tree Withering Connection', 'Both passages emphasize the withering of the fig tree, demonstrating the disciples'' astonishment at its rapid decay. The mention of the fig tree in both texts highlights the significance of Jesus'' actions and the disciples'' reactions.', 'parallel', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
